<number id="3DBB24B2B2581A6AFBC5FF69FB98FF78" box="[1032,1085,188,212]" pageId="2" pageNumber="196" value="0.13">0.13</number>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C369651EB2581A6CFF0AFF0AFA39FC08" lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="198" pageId="2" pageNumber="196" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCC3695B2581A6AFF0AFF0AFC60FEB0" blockId="2.[151,1436,151,285]" pageId="2" pageNumber="196">
<emphasis id="B907EA87B2581A6AFF0AFF0AFE32FF54" bold="true" box="[199,407,223,248]" pageId="2" pageNumber="196">General coloring.</emphasis>
Dorsally dark brown with yellowish stripes on the thorax and dark brown abdomen, ventral side very pale; brown markings of the wings restricted to the apical area.
</paragraph>
