</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCC3695B25E1A6CFF0AFC2DFD02FBFB" blockId="4.[151,1436,151,1111]" pageId="4" pageNumber="198">
<emphasis id="B907EA87B25E1A6CFF0AFC2DFE8EFBBC" bold="true" box="[199,299,1016,1040]" pageId="4" pageNumber="198">Ecology.</emphasis>
The bio-ecology of this myrmeleontid is unknown, it appears to be a forest species. In 
<collectingCountry id="F3647605B25E1A6CFA9CFC22FA39FBA3" box="[1361,1436,1015,1039]" name="Gabon" pageId="4" pageNumber="198">Gabon</collectingCountry>
