<number id="3DBB24B2B25E1A6CFB7CFBC9FB68FB98" box="[1201,1229,1052,1076]" pageId="4" pageNumber="198" value="19.0">19</number>
:00 to 
<number id="3DBB24B2B25E1A6CFAD0FBC9FA99FB98" box="[1309,1340,1052,1076]" pageId="4" pageNumber="198" value="22.0">22</number>
:00, in a secondary growth forest (Deiaco pers. comm.).
</paragraph>
